From 0c716be7de1609e3f78d3052a007181f8a69d3a2 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Harshal Dev <harshal.dev@oss.qualcomm.com>
Date: Mon, 12 Jan 2026 18:04:09 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] libckteec: Add tee trace files until minkteec exports them

Added teec_trace.h and teec_trace.c to libckteec library since minkteec
library does not export and install them unlike the optee teec library.

Upstream-Status: Pending

Signed-off-by: Harshal Dev <harshal.dev@oss.qualcomm.com>
---
 libckteec/CMakeLists.txt   |   1 +
 libckteec/src/teec_trace.c | 141 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 libckteec/src/teec_trace.h | 147 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 3 files changed, 289 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 libckteec/src/teec_trace.c
 create mode 100644 libckteec/src/teec_trace.h

diff --git a/libckteec/CMakeLists.txt b/libckteec/CMakeLists.txt
index 978e665..4b6ccc7 100644
--- a/libckteec/CMakeLists.txt
+++ b/libckteec/CMakeLists.txt
@@ -24,6 +24,7 @@ set(SRC
 	src/pkcs11_token.c
 	src/serializer.c
 	src/serialize_ck.c
